We can use the Eclipse Plug-in as well, for UI based debugging of shell-script  
Eclipse Shelled Plug-in:  
  http://sourceforge.net/projects/shelled/files/shelled/update/
bash debugger - only works with shelled:  
  http://sourceforge.net/projects/basheclipse/

Reference(s):  
  https://www.cyberciti.biz/tips/debugging-shell-script.html  
  https://www.baeldung.com/linux/debug-bash-script  
